<item>
            <title>[QPID-193] AMQSession.createConsumer must be synchronous to avoid timing problems</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPID-193</link>
                <project id="12310520" key="QPID">Qpid</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Several people have noticed occasional failure in some tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In particular tests that create multiple connections can fail intermittently. This looks to be some kind of race condition.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12358686">QPID-193</key>
            <summary>AMQSession.createConsumer must be synchronous to avoid timing problems</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
